    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一步：从神秘的巫师手中获取护身符。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第二步：在中世纪的奇幻世界追捕超大号狮鹫。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第三步：挂了？再来！接着再来！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《赴死之路: 法诺拉的狂野之境》 (To The Grave: The Wildlands of Faenora)</strong>是一款战术回合制肉鸽游戏，在这里你要么是天选之子……要么就只是带着护身符与梦想，却最终葬身荒野的又一个炮灰。抉择你的命运，招募你的团队，祈祷这次<i>狮鹫别把大家给</i>“干”掉——当然还有巨龙、莫名其妙戴着手套的巨型腐化熊之类的。<strong></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心玩法：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战术小队&amp;绝地求生：</strong>指挥一帮半吊子冒险家在战棋式回合对决中骚操作。把你的英雄塞进 3x3 九宫格，专挑敌人弱点下手，顺便祈祷别被团灭——没错，是“再次”祈祷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/be99387d82355a6bbd674862007d78ab.poster.avif?t=1771967290\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/be99387d82355a6bbd674862007d78ab.webm?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/be99387d82355a6bbd674862007d78ab.mp4?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>花式武装 or 当场去世（一般武装了也没用）：</strong>给你的队员装备宝剑盔甲、附魔挂件和丑到没眼看的时尚单品。给他们升职转职，解锁炫酷技能，然后假装这一切都在你的天才计划中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/11d2a93e7a8d58dbb3235bcb31da01cc.poster.avif?t=1771967290\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/11d2a93e7a8d58dbb3235bcb31da01cc.webm?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/11d2a93e7a8d58dbb3235bcb31da01cc.mp4?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选路一时爽，选完火葬场：</strong>狂野之境不提供导航，只有受诅咒的战利品、可疑的路人和多到离谱的岔路口。每次冒险都有新事件、新挑战和创意去世的一百种姿势（包的）！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/dd5d93f0bb5fd7dce255217890acaf87.poster.avif?t=1771967290\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/dd5d93f0bb5fd7dce255217890acaf87.webm?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/dd5d93f0bb5fd7dce255217890acaf87.mp4?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战棋的艺术：</strong>前排猛猛干架、后排噌噌射箭，还要小心那个非要横着飘的幽灵。排兵布阵需谨慎，否则翻车等着你。友情提示：远程放前排 = 白给。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/ee47d33ff319fdb7da4825f83aa7322b.poster.avif?t=1771967290\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/ee47d33ff319fdb7da4825f83aa7322b.webm?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053990/extras/ee47d33ff319fdb7da4825f83aa7322b.mp4?t=1771967290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>像素的魔法世界：</strong>扑面而来的奇幻世界里，怪物们长得居然有点好 rua？每个怀旧像素块都在“可爱”和“下一秒黑化”之间疯狂试探。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情的正确打开方式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在法诺拉王国，传说诞生于刀光剑影、巫术魔法，以及一系列不太明智的人生选择。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的冒险从一家小酒馆开始：听说有狮鹫出没？某个动机可疑的巫师硬塞给你一枚“保命”护身符？于是你穷得只剩勇气，拉上临时拼凑的塑料队友，横冲杀入狂野之境——追荣耀！抢宝藏！顺便搞清楚那只狮鹫到底在闹什么脾气！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但狂野之境可不止有巨型鸟怪这么简单。苍郁林海里埋着上古秘辛，深渊魔域里渗出腐化之力，或许……或许还有命中注定要你发现的惊天秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哪怕路上死个几十次又怎样？（反正肯定会的）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入冒险，</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为作死先锋，欢迎加入《赴死之路：法诺拉的狂野之境》 (To The Grave: The Wildlands of Faenora)，<strong>抢先成为被虐千百遍仍待游戏如初恋的勇者！现在加入愿望单，即可预约抢先体验：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在经典等轴像素美学中探索森林地牢；撸到超可爱的小熊猫；用你的花样死法帮开发者完善游戏机制。您的反馈可能拯救无数后来者的生命——当然，不包括您自己。</p>",
